These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, chess, camping, hiking
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, car, motorbike, roller
1. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
2. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
3. the person driving the car is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
5. the person driving the roller is between the person driving the car and the person driving the motorbike##2
6. the person who's hobby is hiking is the person driving the bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |    4     |
| Hobby   | hiking | writing     | camping | chess |
| Transport     | bike     | motorbike | roller  | car      |

