.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-2::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, hip-hop, rock, techno
There are 4 different nationalities: indian, pakistani, french, italian
1. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the pakistani##1
2. the italian is on the far left or far right##3
3. the fan of techno is on the left of the italian##1
4. the italian is on the right of the pakistani##1
5. the fan of rock is on the far right##1
6. the indian is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |   4   |
| Music-Genre   | gospel | hip-hop    | techno     | rock  |
| Nationality     | indian    | french | pakistani | italian |

