.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, collecting, dancing, fishing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, cycling, skiing, handball
1. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the person who's hobby is board-games and the person who's sport is skiing##2
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3
4. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is handball##3
5. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
6. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |
| Hobby         | collecting | board-games | fishing | dancing  |
| Sport   | cycling  | tennis   | handball  | skiing |

