.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, fanta, hot-chocolate, soy-milk
4 different pets are kept: turtle, bird, rabbit, snake
1. the owner of the bird is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
3. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the owner of the bird##3
4. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
5. the owner of the snake is the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | 7up    | fanta   | hot-chocolate | soy-milk    |
| Pet      | bird | turtle | rabbit       | snake |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta, juice, soy-milk
There 4 different types of food: kale, grapefruit, apple, apricot
1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
2. the person eating apple is between the person eating apricot and the person drinking juice##2
3. the person eating kale is between the person eating apple and the person drinking coffee##2
4. the person eating apricot is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2   |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage    | coffee | juice | soy-milk | fanta |
| Food   | grapefruit | kale  | apple    | apricot  |

