3. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
4. the indian is between the french and the thai##2
5. the person drinking water is the person drinking water##1
6. the person drinking water is between the person drinking cola and the thai##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |  2   |   3    |     4      |
| Nationality   | egyptian | thai | indian | french     |
| Beverage     | hot-chocolate | soy-milk  | water   | cola |

