.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-10::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, electronic, jazz, salsa
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: rose, orchid, daffodil, aconite
1. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
2. the fan of jazz is between the person who growsaconite and the person who growsorchid##2
3. the fan of electronic is the person who growsorchid##1
4. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
5. the fan of salsa is on the left or right of the person who growsrose##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3     |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | classical | electronic | jazz      | salsa   |
| Flower   | daffodil  | orchid    | rose | aconite |

