2. the social-worker is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
3. the person driving the tram is the dancer##1
4. the dancer is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3
5. the person driving the tram is on the left or right of the dressmaker##3
6. the person driving the taxi is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Job       | dressmaker | dancer | entrepreneur    | social-worker      |
| Transport   | taxi       | tram       | snowmobile | skateboard |

