.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-12::.
City: hamburg, liverpool, nizza, paris
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, hamster, rat, turtle
1. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
3. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
4. the person traveling to hamburg is on the far left##1
5. the person traveling to nizza is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |      3      |   4    |
| City   | hamburg     | liverpool  | paris | nizza |
| Pet     | guinea-pig | turtle | hamster     | rat    |

