.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-13::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, canadian, german, turkish
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, van, bus, roller
1. the canadian is on the far right##1
2. the american is the american##1
3. the person driving the van is on the left or right of the person driving the quad-bike##3
4. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left or right of the canadian##3
5. the german is on the left or right of the turkish##3
6. the person driving the van is on the left or right of the turkish##3
7. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person driving the roller##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3    |    4     |
| Nationality   | american | german  | turkish | canadian |
| Transport           | bus     | roller | quad-bike    | van     |

