.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-14::.
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, cabbage, plum, potato
4 different games are played: billiard, mah-jongg, monopoly, poker
1. the person eating potato is on the left or right of the person playing mah-jongg##3
2. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
3. the person eating cabbage is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
4. the person playing mah-jongg is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person eating plum is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Food   | cabbage  | artichoke | potato  | plum      |
| Game    | poker | billiard | monopoly | mah-jongg |

