.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-16::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, canadian, polish, turkish
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, april, june, january
1. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in september##3
2. the turkish is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in january##3
3. the american is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in june##3
4. the turkish is on the left of the polish##1
5. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Nationality   | american | turkish | polish | canadian |
| Birthday         | april  | june   | january | september     |

