.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-17::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: volleyball, cycling, rugby, baseball
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, dubstep, indie, punk
1. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
2. the fan of punk is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
3. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left or right of the fan of dubstep##3
4. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the fan of disco##1
5. the fan of indie is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |   3   |   4   |
| Sport      | volleyball | cycling    | baseball  | rugby |
| Music-Genre   | disco       | dubstep | indie | punk  |

