.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-18::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, horror, satire, spy
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, biathlon, handball, skateboarding
1. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
2. the person watching horror movies is the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
3. the person watching horror movies is on the left or right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##3
4. the person watching spy movies is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who's sport is handball is between the person watching spy movies and the person who's sport is skateboarding##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3      |  4  |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | horror  | animation  | spy |
| Sport           | ice-hockey    | skateboarding | handball | biathlon |

