.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta, milk, soy-milk
House: victorian, art-deco, ranch-style, craftsman
1. the ranch-style house is on the far right##1
2. the craftsman house is the craftsman house##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the craftsman house##3
4. the victorian house is on the far left or far right##3
5. the craftsman house is on the left or right of the ranch-style house##3
6. the victorian house is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
7. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the ranch-style house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4     |
| Beverage   | fanta     | cola     | milk          | soy-milk |
| House      | victorian | art-deco | craftsman | ranch-style  |

 